y: 0.5\">, </span><a style=\"opacity: 0.5; opacity: 0.5\" href=\"http://hl7.org/cda/stds/core/2.0.1-sd/StructureDefinition-II.html\">II</a><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\">, </span><a style=\"opacity: 0.5; opacity: 0.5\" href=\"http://hl7.org/cda/stds/core/2.0.1-sd/StructureDefinition-TEL.html\">TEL</a><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\">, </span><a style=\"opacity: 0.5; opacity: 0.5\" href=\"http://hl7.org/cda/stds/core/2.0.1-sd/StructureDefinition-AD.html\">AD</a><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\">, </span><a style=\"opacity: 0.5; opacity: 0.5\" href=\"http://hl7.org/cda/stds/core/2.0.1-sd/StructureDefinition-EN.html\">EN</a><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\">, </span><a style=\"opacity: 0.5; opacity: 0.5\" href=\"http://hl7.org/cda/stds/core/2.0.1-sd/StructureDefinition-INT.html\">INT</a><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\">, </span><a style=\"opacity: 0.5; opacity: 0.5\" href=\"http://hl7.org/cda/stds/core/2.0.1-sd/StructureDefinition-REAL.html\">REAL</a><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\">, </span><a style=\"opacity: 0.5; opacity: 0.5\" href=\"http://hl7.org/cda/stds/core/2.0.1-sd/StructureDefinition-PQ.html\">PQ</a><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\">, </span><a style=\"opacity: 0.5; opacity: 0.5\" href=\"http://hl7.org/cda/stds/core/2.0.1-sd/StructureDefinition-MO.html\">MO</a><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\">, </span><a style=\"opacity: 0.5; opacity: 0.5\" href=\"http://hl7.org/cda/stds/core/2.0.1-sd/StructureDefinition-TS.html\">TS</a><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\">, </span><a style=\"opacity: 0.5; opacity: 0.5\" href=\"http://hl7.org/cda/stds/core/2.0.1-sd/StructureDefinition-IVL-PQ.html\">IVL_PQ</a><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\">, </span><a style=\"opacity: 0.5; opacity: 0.5\" href=\"http://hl7.org/cda/stds/core/2.0.1-sd/StructureDefinition-IVL-TS.html\">IVL_TS</a><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\">, </span><a style=\"opacity: 0.5; opacity: 0.5\" href=\"http://hl7.org/cda/stds/core/2.0.1-sd/StructureDefinition-PIVL-TS.html\">PIVL_TS</a><span style=\"opacity: 0.5\">, </span><a style=\"opacity: 0.5; opacity: 0.5\" 